title: 8 Rare 80s Albums [Part 89] New Wave, Rock, Power Pop
description:
These eight records are all requested; either here in comments or by e-mail. Anyhow they are here to grab and enjoy! call it an early xmas gift if you want to lol. If you have an 80s record request, drop me a line.

Fiction Factory - Another Story [1985]
